Class Image

    NullImage

    public class Image
extends Notification
    So our program is core on trades, and profiles and users. Users have profiles and there is a very clear way to make their profiles and their offers (of skills) more lucrative, exciting, cool and overall appleaing... Colorful images! We're going to actually grant the user the ability to actually go through their application and select an image (or upload a new one!) where they will be making an image class.
